folder: New Lots Avenue & Jerome Street, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Jerome Street
text:
New Lots Ave., south side, east of Jerome Street, showing across the cemetery, the New Lots Dutch Reformed Church. This church was established in 1824. The Sunday School is just beyond the church.
About 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
